cast.overview: A family discovers that dark spirits have invaded their home after their son inexplicably falls into an endless sleep. When they reach out to a professional for help, they learn things are a lot more personal than they thought.
cast.title: Insidious

details.biography: Corbett Tuck  (born March 4, 1977) is an American actress and screenwriter. She is most known for roles in "Insidious" (2010) and "Insidious: Chapter 3" (2015). She also co-wrote the horror film "Wolf Man" (2025).  She has been married to filmmaker Leigh Whannell.
details.name: Corbett Tuck
